You've gotten this far, you know the drill. You've made more circuits than you can count, but what if that isn't enough? It's time to stop scaling the old way, and start manufacturing like the late game engineer you are.

The Nanochip Assembly Complex isn't just a fancier CAL or Assembly Line - it is the core of your entire operation. For the low price of a small craft* for your machines to chew on, you can be the proud owner of the latest innovation in circuit crafting technology! 

§oNote*: "Small craft" may not accurately reflect the state of your industrialization and the company holds no accountability or liability for professional mishaps like "that's way too much UHV Superconductor" or "we need to scale our HILEs yesterday"§r

§oNAC™ sold as-is. Functionality available via separately crafted modules
